## Anushka_daily_progress

***MONTHLY SALES TRENDS***
---------------------------------------------
This is based on the sample dataset which our team lead has provided. 


* This chart shows how total sales change over time on a monthly basis.

* Certain months have higher sales, indicating seasonal demand patterns.

* This helps businesses plan inventory and promotions in peak periods.

## Top 10 Products by Total Sales

This charts tells us about the following:

* A small number of products contribute the majority of total sales.

* These top-performing products are key revenue drivers.

* Focusing on their availability and promotion can increase overall sales.
